title: Pumpkin-shaped wholemeal bread rolls
ingredients: ['600g wholemeal strong bread flour', '10g dried active yeast', '2 tsp mixed herbs (Mediterranean herbs)', '1 teaspoon garlic granules', '2 teaspoons salt', '2 tablespoons olive oil', '350ml lukewarm water', '1/2 teaspoon dried oregano', '6 pecans']
